9074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:57:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f173167e3cd670632501d11473ecd3e9cbc6fc5e","tid":1630250,"uid":311867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:57:45.000Z","msg":"梗係唔停"},{"pid":"846dd91a8e8dd92c9b612d6f88bb5c5a128e03d1","tid":1630250,"uid":16465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:58:10.000Z","msg":"由佢沉啦<br />\n冇意思"},{"pid":"72b11a3988519bd7e75ffbd14a16a3f2e492fcf3","tid":1630250,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:58:18.000Z","msg":"聽日十八區開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae0eeefd7c5d44efaf84872aaa3fd4b3920b301","tid":1630250,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:58:20.000Z","msg":"No, keep going"},{"pid":"93a4f22c0849ece5444743ab2d116fb92b7ac0a3","tid":1630250,"uid":79599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:58:58.000Z","msg":"停一切就唔好諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係可以做得好d<br />\n<br />\n分析下<br />\n緊急法係有試水溫成份<br />\n想睇下香港人仲會唔會係加重上街風險既情況下仲出黎（事實無人理呢條惡法）<br />\n從而決定繼續用定唔用<br />\n所以變左警犬全部放軟手腳<br />\n等你地驚惡法，少人個陣先捉<br />\n又派臥底周圍燒野，爆門，令到畫面係國際戰線唔太好睇<br />\n藍絲出黎召喚神獸<br />\n<br />\n解法：<br />\n一。上街者<strong>快閃</strong>，遇到召喚神獸，記得四肢為主，頭部受傷唔好睇，亦都易暈低，四肢易有永久損傷，亦會更低調，阻嚇作用更大。和理非自己要學下小心比人跟蹤。<br />\n二。隔離有post話跟據曾健超案，法庭要求被襲者要認出襲擊者。如果警察獲法例豁免就會無法被認出，違反法律平等原則。應該申請禁制令禁止豁免  呢個方法幾好，以子之矛，攻子之盾<br />\n三。繼續JR緊急法 唔洗講<br />\n四。火魔法師要記得火係singal要走或要攻，一係好似燒元朗黑警，一係燒黨鐵，一係整定路障，有黑警先放拖時間，盡量減少周圍放<br />\n五。分化，左膠一律當五毛處理<br />\n六。有Twitter團隊，但人唔夠多，要繼續加強，國際比我地既訊息好有用其實<br />\n七。繼續搵仔，分化前線內部，搵到仔既外國巴應該充分利用，唔好咁快公佈，等仔仔供出更多仔仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n八。搵下之前練乙錚個post，瑞士個款可能係香港出路<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%99%E8%B4%8F-%E4%B8%AD%E7%AB%8B%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E7%9A%84%E5%86%8D%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259B%2599%25E8%25B4%258F-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2587%25BA%2F&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6oHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=64405e7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259B%2599%25E8%25B4%258F-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2587%25BA%2F&h=ca098f72\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%99%E8%B4%8F-%E4%B8%AD%E7%AB%8B%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E7%9A%84%E5%86%8D%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA/</a>"},{"pid":"de2fb55fbb68e51572447b364972e9eccfd89db2","tid":1630250,"uid":142771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:59:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不推文屌柒你老母</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"574c591e23397a2ec041c09a161c85f04ec5b617","tid":1630250,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fe14d07bd413ca9fe797d4352ea4c2732c4238f","tid":1630250,"uid":22967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:54:06.000Z","msg":"拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:59:37.000Z","msg":"唔好拉住 出面大愛post 又千幾正評 勇武post 又千幾正評<br />\n<br />\n就用呢個post 睇究竟